<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.10">
<l>kaḻiyamikkatōr kātala ḷivaḷeṉ ṟaṉṉai kāṇakkoṭāḷ</l>
<l>vaḻuvil kīrttit tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>kuḻumit tēvar kuḻāṅkaṭoḻac cōtiveḷ ḷattiṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>yeḻuvatō ruruveṉ ṉeñcuḷḷeḻu mārkku maṟivaritē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Exceedingly much in love [is] she”, so mother doesn’t let [me be] seen.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with faultless fame,</l>
<l>a form arises in my heart, that rises in a flood of light,</l>
<l>for throngs of gods to gather [and] worship, difficult to understand for anybody.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
